Apache2-AuthzCaps version 0.001
===============================

Apache2::AuthzCaps is a perl module which provides simple Apache2 capability-based authorization. It contains a PerlAuthzHandler and some utility functions.

Please read the Apache2::AuthzCaps POD for detailed information.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

- mod_perl2
- YAML::Any

